&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Tracks and reports transformation and continuous improvement benefits realization (cost saving, cycle time reduction, quality improvements)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
