&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Supports the design and development of bespoke aircraft interiors that balance aesthetics, functionality, safety, and manufacturability.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Assists in creating design concepts through research, sketching, inspiration imagery, mood boards, and presentation materials.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Works closely with Designers and Design Integrators to create and revise floor plans, interior elevations, sections, and detailed drawings using AutoCAD and Rhino.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
