&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Collaborates with Engineering, Manufacturing, Supply Chain, Program Management, and Installation teams to support design development and problem-solving.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
