&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Analyzes and interprets subsystem and project specifications.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Selects materials for mechanical designs based on structural needs and materials specifications.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
